  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators compare two techniques for laparoscopic sleeve gastrectomy. in the first
      one the distal margin of stapling is 2 cm from the pylorus and in the second it is 6 cm away
      from the pylorus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
